==Usage== <!--T:6-->

<!--T:7-->
# There are several ways to invoke the tool:
#* Press the {{Button|[[Image:TechDraw_ExtensionSelectLineAttributes.svg|16px]] [[TechDraw_ExtensionSelectLineAttributes|Select Line Attributes, Cascade Spacing and Delta Distance]]}} button.
#* Select the {{MenuCommand|TechDraw → Attributes/Modifications → [[Image:TechDraw_ExtensionSelectLineAttributes.svg|16px]] Select Line Attributes, Cascade Spacing and Delta Distance}} option from the menu.
# The {{MenuCommand|Select Line Attributes}} task panel opens.
# Optionally change the {{MenuCommand|Line style}}, the {{MenuCommand|Line width}} and the {{MenuCommand|Line color}}.
# Optionally change the {{MenuCommand|Cascade spacing}}. The [[TechDraw_Workbench#Attributes/Modifications|Cascade Dimension tools]] and the [[TechDraw_Workbench#Format/Organize_Dimensions|Coordinate Dimension tools]] use this value.
# Optionally change the {{MenuCommand|Delta distance}}. The [[Image:TechDraw_ExtensionExtendLine.svg|16px]] [[TechDraw_ExtensionExtendLine|TechDraw ExtensionExtendLine]] tool and [[Image:TechDraw_ExtensionShortenLine.svg|16px]] [[TechDraw_ExtensionShortenLine|TechDraw ExtensionShortenLine]] tool use this value.
# Press the {{Button|OK}} button.

==Notes== <!--T:8-->

<!--T:9-->
* The specified values will be used in the current FreeCAD session only.


